#contain-paint {
  contain: paint;
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  background: red;
}

#child {
  background: green;
  box-shadow: 0 0 100px 100px red;
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
}
</style>
<p>Test passes if there is a filled green square and <style><strong>no red</strong></style>.</p>
